These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
There 2 different types of food: onion, strawberry
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: weightlifting, skiing
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is skiing is not the person eating strawberry##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | strawberry   | onion  |
| Sport   | weightlifting | skiing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
There 2 different types of food: papaya, radish
2 different pets are kept: rat, hedgehog
1. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the owner of the rat is not the person eating radish##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | papaya | radish      |
| Pet    | rat  | hedgehog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-3::.
