.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-7::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  dancer, teacher
2 different pets are kept: rat, horse
1. the dancer is in an odd position##4
2. the dancer is not the owner of the horse##6

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1      |       2       |
| Job   | dancer | teacher |
| Pet   | rat       | horse       |

